name: YOLO FINAL PART I
description:
You may like summer or not, but the truth is that when the hot seasons begin, the scene changes. The flowers are born, the energies rise and everything looks much more beautiful. Change comes, something ends but new adventures arise.
This collection ends, but it is the beginning of new experiences and although its objective is clear, to share my art with you, it always tried to remind me of the beautiful things in life, the things that are worth living for. You only live once! Be happy in your own way!

...........................................................

This piece is the first part of a work consisting of two illustrations, I recommend purchasing this piece I first, and then Part II
